      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kitab-al-mumin:4:4",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/30/1/4/4",
      "text": [
        " المؤمنُ أخو المؤمن يحِقُّ عليه نصيحتُه ومواساتُه ومَنعُ عدوِّه منه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.muhajir-b-ali": [
          "96. It has been reported that Abu 'Abd Allah (a.s) said: A believer is a brother to another believer and it is his right that he should counsel him, sympathize with him and prevent his enemies from harming him."
        ]
      }
    },
